Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:20.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:27.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Avatar of probationary student{\i0}\N{\i1}Akihisa Yoshii has special features.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only can he touch objects,{\i0}\N{\i1}but by using his augmented strength...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:35.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Go get the world map.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:37.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:40.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...he is forced to help{\i0}\N{\i1}teachers with their chores.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:43.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! Bring the desks\Nto the audio-visual room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:45.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! Move the soccer goalpost back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Again? Why am I the only\None who gets ordered around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's how probationary students are treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:56.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm so ticked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The probationary student receives{\i0}\N{\i1}the same pain his Avatar receives as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:08.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a small test next,\Nso review what you've learned so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll avenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:16.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:27.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hottoite sodatsu mono nanda nandarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one more{\i0}\N{\i1}chance. Never never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance. Never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:46.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deai mashite wa kantan sugiruyo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:48.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saisho ni kimeta kotae wa hitotsu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokimeki mashita goukaku shimasuka?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:54.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koi mo shoubu mo awatenai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotsu kotsu kotsu to tetsuya ni tameiki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watashi no naka ni tensai dreamer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Omou koto mina kanaeba iina{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hito no sekai wa kinishinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zettai koko de matterunda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:16.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area nozomu koe ga kikoeruyo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:17.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! Ear! Ear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? Tomaranai surechigai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:23.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watashi ga soudan aite nara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:26.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Tomodachi kai?" "Tomodachi desu."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanashiki rei ten dane{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Yarinaoshi kakinaoshi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honki de one more chance please{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ima yori suteki na mirai ga arunoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:44.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ima yori suteki ni my life, my life, my life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.34,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 4"\N"Love, Spices, and Boxed Lunches"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:51.75,MainTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today is Sunday. However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:55.68,MainTop,,0,0,0,,This is it for today. Make sure\Nyou review when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...despite that, Year 2,{\i0}\N{\i1}Class F had a remedial class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, Yoshii, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I tried for a little revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:09.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So you got beaten up instead, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:17.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Since he made me do so much\Nwork today, I'm hungrier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Avatar seems convenient,\Nbut he's actually inconvenient, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji. Lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:28.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouko! Why? Class A isn't\Ntaking a remedial class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I was studying by myself. If you're\Nhere, I'll come in even on Sundays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.18,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're not here, I won't come\Nin even during the weekdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.76,Main,,0,0,0,,That can be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... You brought a boxed lunch today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,One sixty-seventh of a cup noodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.56,Main,,0,0,0,,One sixty-seventh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,One half of one half of one half\Nof one half of one half of one half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa, that's one sixty-fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Calculating fractions is\Nyour weak spot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:01.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,How pitiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a lunch that moves you to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:10.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I guess it can't be helped. Would\Nyou like me to share my lunch with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I made too much and brought extra with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be a waste if I ditch it,\Nso do you wanna eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:16.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec, okay? Hm? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:23.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... looks like I left it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:25.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,After all that effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Thinking that you could do a girly\Nthing like making a boxed lunch was my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,spine is being shattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you that I just forgot to bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Almost... Almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,"I can almost see, but not quite"\N"A little further...!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:42.87,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Fingers"\N"Eyes"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ahh! Ouch! My eyes! My eyes!\N--You can't look at it, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.25,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys are lively, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.67,Main,,0,0,0,,--Excuse me...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this Class F, the class for idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hazuki?! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hazuki, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Stupid Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.26,Main,,0,0,0,,How amazing, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I never expected your stupidity\Nto be known to the entire country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Could you at least say "throughout town"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:11.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it! It's Stupid Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hazuki, how do you know Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:18.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Because he'll be my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Stupid Big Brother and I are\Ndating with an eye towards marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akihisa was personally{\i0}\N{\i1}acquainted with Hazuki in the past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will explain how he came{\i0}\N{\i1}to know her some other time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Aki! What'd you\Ndo to my little sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.21,Main,,0,0,0,,We're now starting the inquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! What're all you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,The nature of the crime:\Nthe defendant, Akihisa Yoshii,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,committed a serious crime by dating a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,in clear disobedience of the\NInquisition's pledge of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it true and correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.35,Main,,0,0,0,,True and correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant. Do you have any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Why "last words" before the defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:00.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Guilty. Death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ahh! Hey! Ahh! Stop it! What?!\N--What grade are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ahh! Hey! Ahh! Stop it! What?!\N--I'm in fifth grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,--What're you doing?! Stop it! Stop it!\N--Well, well, you're more sensible than Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.20,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ahh! Don't touch there! Ahh!\N--Ah! Pretty Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.87,Main,,0,0,0,,--But it might feel kinda good. Ahh!\N--Hello, Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what brought you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! Here!\NYou left these at home, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:20.84,Main,,0,0,0,,My boxed lunch! Thanks, Hazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Good... So you brought both.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:29.22,Main,,0,0,0,,See? I wasn't lying. I can make\Nthings like boxed lunches just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:35.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You woke up early, which you\Nrarely do, and made them eagerly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering why.\NNow I know. You wanted Stupid Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I wonder what she's talking\Nabout. What a weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. So you made that\Nboxed lunch for Akihisa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:51.41,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Why would I do that for Aki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Then what were you making eagerly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:57.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That wasn't the boxed lunch. You know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,It was a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:06:59.67,Main,,0,0,0,,A model?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,A one thirty-fifth scale King Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:03.88,Main,,0,0,0,,A German heavy tank...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Akihisa. That's bigger\Nthan one sixty-fourth cup noodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The size isn't in question here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It might unexpectedly taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.18,Main,,0,0,0,,It's an inorganic substance! You can't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, this is just an extra.\NI didn't make it for Aki, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's the matter, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What? No, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that... a boxed lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? You made it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes... though I couldn't make it that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,U... Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:43.17,Main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth... I made this for Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii, if you like, could you eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,We're now starting the inquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:52.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhh?! Hold on... Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Guilty. Death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not even given an\Nopportunity to speak this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Please wait! It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:06.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... Uhm... It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:12.28,Main,,0,0,0,,This boxed lunch was... Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll be tortured and {\i1}then{\i0}... death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:21.04,Main,,0,0,0,,-Ahh! Hey! Whoa! They really started a fire! Ahh! A real fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:25.00,Main,,0,0,0,,--Oh? Big Sis?\N--Ahhhhhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiot Test
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:47.90,Main,,0,0,0,,If it means I can eat the boxed\Nlunch you made, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... How flattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:54.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You can eat it without being interrupted here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna make me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:06.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... I forgot to bring\Nsomething to drink. I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:14.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Himeji is cute, smart, and\Non top of that, she can even cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,She's too good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Yuuji! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:20.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! You too, Hideyoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?\NIt's just one piece. Don't be so stin--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi?! What's the matter, you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad, Muttsulini! We should\Ntake them to the nurse's office!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me this lunch was the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:48.05,Main,,0,0,0,,No way... when it looks so delicious...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:10.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That was close. My soul was almost taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake. They fell\Nbecause of this boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,To think that the smell\Nalone is this dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,A... Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,The plate... Hand me the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"Once you've had poison, you\Nmight as well have the plate, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That saying means that if you\Neat the plate, too, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:38.35,Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad! His thinking ability is paralyzed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I got something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? What happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:48.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... They got sleepy after eating,\Nso they said they'd take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,If you sleep right after\Nyou eat, you'll become a cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:55.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it means staying alive,{\i0}\N{\i1}being a cow may be better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:58.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Th-Thanks, Himeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad... What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,"You'd better eat or Himeji will be sad."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.38,Main,,0,0,0,,"You'd better eat or Himeji will be sad."\N"Don't eat it. There'll be consequences."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.38,Main,,0,0,0,,"...consequences"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:15.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"If you tell the truth, Himeji will be hurt."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"If you tell the truth, Himeji will be hurt."\N"Do you wanna die?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're not eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:23.02,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I feel like this is\Ntoo precious to eat, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,"It's your life that's\Nprecious, right?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be... that it was a bother for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! There's no way that's the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm very glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.19,Main,,0,0,0,,"Your consideration by itself makes me glad."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,"Rather, I'll take just the consideration."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Are you the type who\Nsamples the food while cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:44.16,Main,,0,0,0,,People say that if you sample\Nwhile cooking, you'll gain weight, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:48.67,Main,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to eat it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The paths of retreat are all cut off now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:59.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do the angel and{\i0}\N{\i1}devil have the same opinion?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,A... Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:06.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Himeji. May I have\Nsomething to drink, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Could you go buy oolong tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa... I'll give you some good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:22.74,Main,,0,0,0,,From ancient times, there have\Nexisted many spices used as antidotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.20,Main,,0,0,0,,In the time before refrigerators were available,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,people used the sterilizing\Nability of spices to store food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:33.17,Main,,0,0,0,,And, it is said that in girls'\Ncooking, love is, indeed, the best spice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:35.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you... possibly saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Neutralize the poison\Nwith the spice called love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... I get it, Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:47.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a trial given to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:52.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll overcome\Nany hardship for the sake of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I have the best spice\Ncalled love, no matter what poison it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,So love doesn't have a\Ndetoxifying effect... noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:13.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa is a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? What happened to Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:21.01,Main,,0,0,0,,He said he got sleepy since he ate lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,If you sleep right after\Nyou eat, you'll become a cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:29.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, what happened to Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.44,Main,,0,0,0,,After all that effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish I had been honest\Nand asked him to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:46.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I never thought that Himeji would\Nhave a subject that she's bad at.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm hungrier now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:55.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Stupid Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know where my sister went?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:03.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Haven't you had lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:10.60,Main,,0,0,0,,A lot happened and I couldn't consume calories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Then are you starving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:17.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... If only I had the\Nboxed lunch that Minami made...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,My Big Sister's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was wondering what kind\Nof lunch she made. I wanted to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:27.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki! Have this lunc--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.66,Main,,0,0,0,,M-Miharu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I looked all over for you, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:37.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I did my utmost in making\NMiharu's Special Lunch. Please have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:41.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?! Class D\Nisn't having a remedial class, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:43.72,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're here, I'll come in even on Sundays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:45.93,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're not here, I won't\Ncome in even during the weekdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:49.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is this academy full of students\Nwith messed up common sense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Nooooow, honey! Let's spend\Na happy afternoon together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.39,Main,,0,0,0,,--Anyway, shall we look for her that way first?\N--Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,--Anyway, shall we look for her that way first?\N--I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:55.69,Main,,0,0,0,,--Okay!\N--I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:59.02,Main,,0,0,0,,--Let's be alone and feed each other!\N--No! Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:05.11,Main,,0,0,0,,"Fire Hydrant"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez. She doesn't have to be so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Honey! Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That darn Miharu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:20.79,Main,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I have to find Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Haiseiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't run in the corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki... Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,This time for sure, I'll give him this lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,So it was true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:16:02.04,Main,,0,0,0,,So Yoshii has got two\Ngirls making lunch for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.59,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the unforgivable truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring death to the traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring death to the traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:10.85,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No! That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.18,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This is... uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:25.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--Guilty! Guilty!\N--What?! What?! Hey! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You've all got messed up common sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:34.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez... What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Haru Urara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:38.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Run at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't run in the corridor, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't a corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm already out of gas today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time for sure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:49.88,Main,,0,0,0,,--Aki!\N--Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Minami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm playing with Stupid Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,That's good. But don't bother him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Aki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Did you already have lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:08.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I have... or should I say I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:13.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:17.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... if you're hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:21.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Wh... Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:33.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the local specialty of Oshamanbe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:36.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, shoot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,The local specialty of Oshamanbe,\NHokkaido, would be horsehair crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Kubo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.02,Main,,0,0,0,,To see that you're at school on Sunday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you studying by yourself, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Class F had a remedial class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? You haven't had lunch yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? N-Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, would you care to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What? But I don't have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, well, it can't be helped, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Since it's just lunch,\NI don't mind treating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go! I'll definitely go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, see you later, Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:11.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't we prepare for\Nmid-terms together while eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Mid-terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Hazuki, have you had lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:25.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, playing with\NBig Brother made me forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:29.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez. You shouldn't skip meals\Nor you won't be able to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't this for Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,No. There's no way that's the\Ncase, is there? I made this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, let's eat together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:44.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:48.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hazuki. I forgot that we\Nstill have another remedial class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lunch A looks the best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or should I be considerate and get Lunch B?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:14.61,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Seasoned Laver Paste"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fukuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:19.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Good timing. I've got a\Nproblem. I can't open the lid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Could you have your Avatar open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:28.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm summoning my Avatar. Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who died with their score reduced\Nto zero will be given a remedial class!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why?! I haven't eaten anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:54.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--That's all because of your low viability.\N--How cute Yoshii is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What am I saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I shall eat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Idiot Aki! You're really an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:22.51,Main,,0,0,0,,An ultra idiot! A heaping idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:27.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Who'd make lunch for you?!\NWho would?! Who would?!
