Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:02.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you... going to ditch that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I don't think people\Nshould waste resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,For alleviating global warming\Nas well, you shouldn't waste food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,If you waste food, the\Nwaste-not ghost will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, to help the ecosystem, you\Nshould recycle, or how should I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.55,Main,,0,0,0,,we should use our limited\Nresources more effectively...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,that's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,--Here.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you going to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, then, I guess I'll eat it.\NWe shouldn't waste our resour--
